pr_description:
This strips spaces and comments from query text before hashing them so that 

```
{
  site {
    siteMetadata {
      github
    }
  }
}
```

is the same as 

```
            {
              site {
                siteMetadata {
                  github
                }
              }
            }

```

This will lead to better caching and query reuse 🙂

