pr_description:
Closes #9235 

Implements the following comments directive to declare lines to highlights in `gatsby-remark-prismjs`:

- `highlight-line` highlights the current line;
- `highlight-next-line` highlights the next line;
- `highlight-start` highlights the lines until the matching `hightlight-end`;
- `highlight-range{1, 4-6}` will highlight the next line, and the fourth, fifth and sixth lines.

Also refactors `gatsby-remark-embed-snippet` to rely on this implementation of the directive instead of a local one.

Thanks @DSchau for the headstart :)
